flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic review of returnable packaging inventory and usage data.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest returnable container usage data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Stream: STREAMS - Analyze usage patterns and inventory levels using STREAMS.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Cortex Auto Forecast - Determine optimal fleet sizing and allocation using Cortex Auto Forecast.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Process Builder - Schedule collection and consolidation actions using Process Builder.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: Process Builder - Schedule cleaning and maintenance activities using Process Builder.]
  N5 --> N6[Stream: STREAMS - Track and prevent loss of returnable packaging using STREAMS.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced working capital, lower COGS, improved order fulfillment OTIF, and minimized reliance on one-way packaging.]
  N3 -->|High inventory levels detected| B1[Trigger additional collection and consolidation actions.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Reduced excess inventory and optimized working capital.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Low inventory levels detected| B2[Increase fleet sizing and expedite collection actions.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Ensured timely availability of returnable assets.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Maintenance backlog exceeds threshold| B3[Prioritize and expedite cleaning and maintenance schedules.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Minimized downtime and ensured usable returnables.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]